This directory contains scripts to handle the upgrade from PostGIS 2.4.9 or 2.5.5 to
2.5.9. All of these scripts MUST be kept together in one directory for them
to work.

After upgrading the system's RPMs and with PostgreSQL running, run
upgrade_postgis.sh as root. Do not interrupt the script while it is running, as
this may prevent proper cleanup. Verify that no errors appear in the output.
